ibrokerkit.iservicestore.store
Interface Locator

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<IService>, IService, java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractLocator, DbLocator
public interface Locator
extends IService

A Locator i-service. Each Locator i-service holds a textual address and description about a user's physical location. In addition, it holds coordinates (lat, lng, zoom) which can be used to draw the user's location on a map.
